# 💾 System Images for Bumblebee

This folder contains Raspberry Pi system images for the Bumblebee drone.

Flash the image to an SD card and insert it into the drone's Raspberry Pi — no additional setup required.

For flashing instructions and image changelog:
👉 **[Bumblebee Students Wiki](https://github.com/ermoluk/bumblebee-students/wiki)**

## Flashing the Image

```bash
# Flash using dd (replace /dev/sdX with your SD card)
sudo dd if=rpi_bumblebee.img of=/dev/sdX bs=4M status=progress
```

Or use **[Raspberry Pi Imager](https://www.raspberrypi.com/software/)** for a simpler experience.
